      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiꞥſch pahrzelt Laikus un Stundas/ wiꞥſch nozelt Kehnixus/ un apſtiprina Kehnixus/ wiꞥſch dohd teem Gudreem Gudribu/un Sinnaschana teem/ kam gudrs Prahts irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch parahda dſtkaß un apſlehptas Leetas/ wiꞥſch ſinna/ kas Tumfiba irr/ jo pee wiꞥſka dſihwo ta Gatsina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es vateizu um teizu tew mannun Tehwu Deewß/ ka tu man Gudribu un Spehku dewiß/ un eſſi man nu ſinnamu darrijs/ ko mehs no tewis eſſam luhgufschi/ jo tu eſſi mums ta Kehnixa Leetu ſinnamu darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje Dantjels pee Arioka/ kam tas Kehnixsch bij pawehlejs tohs Gudrusceksch Babeles nokant/ wiꞥſch nogahje/ un fazzija ta us winnu: Ne noinaita tohs Gudrusceksch Babeles/ wedd mannt pee ta Kehnixa eekſcha/ jo es darriſcha tam Kehnixam to Jsſtahſtischana ſinnamu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad wedde Arioks Dantjelu drths eekſcha pee ta Kehnixa/ un ruunaaja ta us winnu: Es efnn weenu Wihrn no teem Aiswesteein no Juhda atraddis/ kas tam Kehnixam to Jsſtahſtiſchanu fazzijß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Kehnixsch atbildeja/ un fazzija us Dantjelu/ ko tee par Belsazeru nofauze: Wojtu spehji man to Saput ſtahſticht/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Dantjels atbildeja preekſch ta Kehnixa/ un fazzija: To Noſſlehpuu/ ko tas kehnixsch praſſa/ ne warr tee Gudree/ Swaigsnu Zeenitaji/ Sihneeki nedß Pa redſetaji tam Kehninam fazzijt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Deetws ween Deb befiß/ kaß Noſſlehpuuus parahda/ tas irr tam Kehnixam Nebukadnezarain ſinnamu darrijs/ kaß pastara Laika notiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Taws Sapnis/ un kaß ta wai Galwai us tawu Gultu rah dijahs/ irr tchs: Tu kehnixsch us tawu Gultu gulledains dohmaji/ kaß pehz notiks/ un tag/ kaß apſlehptas Leetas parahda/ irr tew ſinnamu darrijs/ kaß pehz notiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Man tad/ man irr tas Noſſlehpuuns varahdihts/ ue zaur to Gudribu/ kaß eekſch mannim/ itt ka buhtu ta leelaka neka zittu/ kaß dſihwo/ bet tapehz/ ka tam kehnixam ta Jsſtahſtischana tapru ſinnama darrita/ un tu ta was Sirde Dohmas warretu ſinnaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Kehnixsch redſeji/ un raugi/ weena leela Bilde bija/ (ta Bilde bija skaista/ un winnas Spohſchums bija leels/) ta ſtahweja tew pretti/ un winnas Sihtis bija breetmigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis Bildes Galwa bija no labba Selta/ winnas Krahts un winnas Rohka no\n"
    }
  ],
